{"tid":2050460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【請留底廣傳】文匯報1989年的六四特刊","createTime":"2020-06-04T06:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T09:56:25.000Z","uid":7542,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6909a8179a846b52fe4f745ba69f91ef57e0e68","tid":2050460,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjFDfBG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjFDfBG.jpg&h=a3072000&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n這是文匯報1989年的六四特刊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Af7Tqi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Af7Tqi.png&h=205c8c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n失控狂笑的解放軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E2iYfDw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE2iYfDw.png&h=c50676b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全埸熄燈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nv0f2ix.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNv0f2ix.png&h=f72b384e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平射手無寸鐵民眾 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGhx4wT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnGhx4wT.png&h=e19229be&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n軍隊要求民眾自行保管武器<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9BV2iz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9BV2iz.png&h=d644a0c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nThe Tank Man<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZxBMLg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZxBMLg.png&h=4a47ab8b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毛澤東與黑絲帶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xy0PniC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXy0PniC.png&h=f57b321